name: W-O-M-E-N
description: Beautiful girl There is no need for anyone to judge. She sometimes even has tattoos to decorate her body. But her elaboration of those tattoos Maybe just because she wanted to symbolize the memories of the depths of her heart to reinforce the stories. She is still beautiful and will always have people who admire and love her, like an insect still in love with a flower. No matter how different the flower is from other flowers.
